Eru, the Evlish name for the Father of All, from whom the Ainur had their being. Through the Music of the Ainur, Eru created Middle Earth and the beings who inhabit it. This Well is believed to be the place where the music of the Ainur was first heard by a living creature of Middle Earth. Bards and Monks tend to discount this theory.
